# Jenkins CI/CD Pipeline

## Architecture

```
GitHub (PR/push) → Jenkins (build) → Harbor (registry) → ArgoCD (deploy)
```

- **Jenkins**: `jenkins.multiagent.vision` (Cloudflare Tunnel — proxmox-tunnel)
- **Harbor**: `registry.multiagent.vision` (external). **Jenkins push** uses `registry.multiagent.vision` with `hostAliases` (→ ingress IP 10.0.0.201) to bypass CF for token endpoint; `--skip-tls-verify` for Kaniko.
- **ArgoCD**: Manages apps from gitops repo; ApplicationSets derive image tags from repo metadata (no gitops update)

